title: Ep. - 216 - DONNIE WAHLBERG AND JENNY MCCARTHY
description:
Donnie Wahlberg reviews a series of shows on the AWE network called Selling Yachts, Selling Jets, and Selling Yachts. Jenny (and Donnie) also review The Staircase on Netflix, about the defense of Michael Peterson in the death of his wife Kathleen. 


Steve Stauff reviews Flirty Dancing on Fox. 


Kate's daughter Hayes reviews Sugar Rush Holiday on Netflix.
